               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180506-54-person498">
                  JOHN 
                  COOPER
               <interp inst="t18180506-54-person498" type="surname" value="COOPER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-54-person498" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-54-person498" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was employed to watch the rick. On the 5th of April, between four and five o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came and made up a bundle out of the rick, and put it on his shoulder, carried it about a hundred yards, and put it down by Carter's stable-door, I then stopped him. He said he took it to lay on-it weighed 40 lbs.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180506-54-person499">
